    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, presenting as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, consistent shine and zero imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine state with no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. It has been meticulously garaged and maintained to the highest standards, making it an ideal choice for a collector or a buyer seeking a like-new experience. Every mechanical and electronic feature functions perfectly, and the engine bay is spotless.",
      "price": 48500.0,
